      <title>Constellation Energy首席执行官关税，核电，能源投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-10/constellation-energy-ceo-on-tariffs-nuclear-power-energy-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[星座能源公司首席执行官乔·多明格斯（Joe Dominguez）谈到了美国贸易战争和关税如何影响能源投资，能源领域的交易，电力需求的未来以及核电的增长。他在休斯敦的Ceraweek与彭博社的Alix Steel进行了交谈（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-10/constellation-energy-ceo-on-tariffs-nuclear-power-energy-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 14:49:40 GMT</pubDate>
