    <item>
      <title>火箭以17.5亿美元的全股票购买Redfin</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-10/rocket-to-buy-redfin-in-1-75-billion-all-stock-deal-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Rocket Cos。已同意在一项价值17.5亿美元的房地产上市网站的交易中购买Redfin Corp.，每笔股票中的每份Redfin股票都在全股交易中支付12.50美元。火箭公司首席执行官Varun Krishna讨论了有关“彭博公开兴趣”的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-10/rocket-to-buy-redfin-in-1-75-billion-all-stock-deal-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 14:46:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
